  "body": "<!-- Start -->\n<div align=center>\n\n<img alt=\"Photon logo\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"/>\n\n# Photon\n\nMinecraft optimization framework prioritizing performance, simplicity, and compatibility. 1.7.10-26.1.2 across Fabric, Forge, NeoForge, and Quilt!\n\n[![GitHub Link](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e8f8bd35e58faad92f3b89dc46803743636b5426_0.webp)](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon)\n[![Wiki Link](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0b84619296c5f5b1898966356b8fd54b01454884.png)](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon/wiki)\n\n[![Mod Request Link](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a9e0e1b13634300da95bf796f06feb70918e1aba.png)](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon/issues/new?template=mod-request.yml)\n[![Bug Report Link](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/41216560b7386b014e2b627db5c02b164ae2aa9f.png)](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon/issues/new?template=bug-report.yml)\n\n[![Modlist Link](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ae06c842cc1ee6832645f1de52406f0cf56644ff.png)](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon/blob/main/MODLIST.md)\n\n</div>\n\nPhoton is a client-side modpack that dramatically improves performance on Minecraft 1.7.10-26.1.2 across Fabric, Forge, NeoForge, and Quilt. Photon is deliberately built with simplicity and compatibility in mind. As a result, Photon can be used as a framework for building larger, content-focused modpacks.\n\n<!--Download-->\n## Download\n\n[![Modrinth Page Link](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e3ccef7ecef76d70a33ed12b65821f810da97b13.png)](https://modrinth.com/modpack/phtn)\n\n<!--Compatibility-->\n## Compatibility\n\n| MC Version | Fabric | Forge | NeoForge | Quilt |\n|------------|:------:|:-----:|:--------:|:-----:|\n| 26.1.2     |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ✅   |   ✅  |\n| 26.1/26.1.1|   ⚠️  |   ❌  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.21.11    |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ✅   |   ✅  |\n| 1.21.5-10  |   ⚠️  |   ❌  |    ⚠️   |   ⚠️  |\n| 1.21.4     |   ⚠️  |   ❌  |    ⚠️   |   ❌  |\n| 1.21.1     |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ✅   |   ✅  |\n| 1.20.6     |   ⚠️  |   ❌  |    ⚠️   |   ⚠️  |\n| 1.20.4     |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ✅   |   ✅  |\n| 1.20.1     |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ✅   |   ✅  |\n| 1.19.4     |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ✅  |\n| 1.18.2     |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ✅  |\n| 1.17.1     |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.16.5     |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.15.2     |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.14.4     |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.12.2     |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.11.2     |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.10.2     |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.9.4      |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.8.9      |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n| 1.7.10     |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ❌   |   ❌  |\n\n✅ = Actively Supported\n⚠️ = Previously Supported\n❌ = Not Supported\n\n**Note: These statuses are subject to change in relation to demand. You may request support for a Minecraft version [here](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon/issues/new?template=version-request.yml).**\n\n---\n\n\n***For benchmarks, credits, and an installation guide—including for preexisting modpacks—please visit the [wiki](https://github.com/RealWTBking/photon/wiki)!***",
